txt.en: While exploring the ancient Elf-harbour of Edhellond, you have encountered a substantial force of Corsairs. They must be defeated before they can pillage more of Gondor's history and bring more harm to the people of Gondor.
You have defeated many Corsairs in Edhellond.
Corsairs of Umbar under the command of The Scourge have made landfall in Edhellond and seek to raid the Havens of Belfalas unhindered.

Corsairs can be found throughout Edhellond in north-west Belfalas.\n\nYou have encountered a large force of Corsairs occupying Edhellond. They must be defeated before they can bring more harm to the people of Gondor.

You have defeated many of the Corsairs in Edhellond. Although the Corsair forces continue to make landfall, you have slowed their assault on the Havens of Belfalas and aided in the protection of Dol Amroth.
